     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\"><hr/><p><b>English</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ConceptMap FRMedicationAdministrationLMCDAFHIR</b></p><a name=\"en-FRMedicationAdministrationLMCDAFHIR\"> </a><a name=\"en-hcFRMedicationAdministrationLMCDAFHIR\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Group 1 </b>Mapping from <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-lm-traitement</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-traitement</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRLMTraitement</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDATraitement</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMTraitement.identifiant</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDATraitement.id</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMTraitement.code</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDATraitement.code</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMTraitement.note</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDATraitement.text</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMTraitement.status</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDATraitement.statusCode</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMTraitement.occurancePeriod</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDATraitement.effectiveTime[not(@operator='A')]</td></tr><tr><td>FRLM